      "text": [
        "4147 - وَ قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"كُلُّ ذِي نَابٍ مِنَ اَلسِّبَاعِ وَ مِخْلَبٍ مِنَ اَلطَّيْرِ حَرَامٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4147 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"Every predatory animal with fangs and every bird with talons is unlawful.\""
        ]
      }
    }
